posts.post_title: 1910 Obak Series of 150 (rare) George Manush SGC SOLD
posts.post_content:
Posted By: Bob
Very nice card. It is the second highest graded Series of 150 Manush, I own the other and it is not for sale any time soon. SGC lists the 150 series and 175 cards together in its population report but to my knowledge only 3 150 Series Manushs have been graded and I own all 3, a 70, a 40 and an Authentic.
No creases. These 150 Series cards are becoming impossible to find. Scan is not the greatest but will give a good idea.
